  TITLE     Purification and characterization of UDP-glucose: anthocyanin 3',5'-O-glucosyltransferase from Clitoria ternatea.
  JOURNAL   Planta. 226 (2007) 1501-9.
  ORGANISM  Clitoria ternatea
PATHWAY     ec00942  Anthocyanin biosynthesis
